      </p></li><li><p>Check <span class="guibutton">"I accept the terms in the Licence Agreement"</span>.</p></li><li><p>Click on <span class="guibutton">Next</span>.       The Choose Setup Type screen is displayed:</p><p>
        <span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="images/guide_install_03.png"></span>
